{"title":"蜀乡行（五首）","authors":["阳翰笙"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":6,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜀乡行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳翰笙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还乡抒怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一别成都六一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如潮往事梦频牵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信百家崇马列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓除魔怪立社团①。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天府今成真天府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴山新胜旧巴山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀欣喜还乡国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老兴欲狂似少年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠谭启龙同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伯乐识得千里马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感君风格比山高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行船还需老舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶扶持红花娇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探望故园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为求真理离家门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来年已逾八旬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍野桑茶翠竹茂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满场②亲友含笑迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一山一水多厚意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一草一木带深情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此去何时再欢聚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依难舍众乡亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"川行途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦绣山河妙手成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯田图案层层新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间谁用大手笔？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术天才是农民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜登枇杷山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万斛明珠落山城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁巧夺天工心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枇杷山上放眼看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯海繁星彻夜明。注：①一九二二年，在《新青年》上看到社会主义青年团章程，我和童庸生、李硕勋、雷兴政、刘弄潮等十余人，自发地组成了社会主义青年团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②“场”，指高县罗场，是我的出生地。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}